 AFRO-SOUL singer and songwriter Elmina hosted fans and friends to an evening of soul-stirring music at the listening party for her new single titled ‘Hold on Me’. The event managed by Tokindrumz Management took place in the Lekki area of Lagos, Nigeria. In attendance were notable contributors to the media and entertainment industry who came out to show their support for the singer. The listening party was held to mark the start of promotion for her upcoming 2021 afro-EP.